quran[7{c,v,t}:
11,6,"zameen mein chalne wala koi jandaar aisa nahi hai jis ka rizaq Allah ke zimmay nah ho aur jis ke mutaliq woh nah jaanta ho ke kahan woh rehta hai aur kahan woh sonpa jata hai, sab kuch aik saaf daftar mein darj hai"
11,7,"aur wohi hai jis ne asmano aur zameen ko chay dinon mein peda kya jabkay is se pehlay is ka arsh pani par tha taakay tum ko aazma kar dekhe tum mein kon behtar amal karne wala hai ab agar ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum kehte ho ke logo, marnay ke baad tum dobarah uthaye jao ge, to munkareen foran bol uthte hain ke yeh to Sarih jaadoo giri hai"
11,8,aur agar hum aik khaas muddat taq un ki saza ko talte hain to woh kehnay lagtay hain ke aakhir kis cheez ne ussay rok rakha hai? suno! jis roz uss saza ka waqt agaya to woh kisi ke phairay nah phir sakay ga aur wohi cheez un ko aa ghairay gi jis ka woh mazaq ura rahay hain
11,9,agar kabhi hum ensaan ko apni rehmat se nawazne ke baad phir is se mahroom kar dete hain to woh mayoos hota hai aur nashukri karne lagta hai
11,10,"aur agar uss museebat ke baad jo uss par aayi thi hum usay Nemat ka maza chukhatay hain to kehta hai mere to saaray dldr paar ho gay, phir woh phoola nahi samata aur akarnay lagta hai"
11,11,is aib se pak agar koi hain to bas woh log jo sabr karne walay aur naiko car hain aur wohi hain jin ke liye dar guzar bhi hai aur bara ajar bhi
11,12,"to aePeghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam kahin aisa nah ho ke tum unn cheezon mein se kisi cheez ko ( bayan kar ne se ) chore do jo tumhari taraf wahi ki ja rahi hain aur iss baat par dil tang ho ke woh kahin ge"" is shakhs par koi khazana kyun nah utaara gaya"" ya yeh ke"" is ke sath koi farishta kyun nah aaya"" tum to mehez khabardaar karne walay ho, agay har cheez ka hawala daar Allah hai"
